TEXT.S: Ed Beach nalecuhan i American, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput. Ed Beach i 1950 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 5 ku uwac atu silsil 59, namapili' tu nu Minneapolis Lakers putiput. 1 bulad 25 demiad, 1993 a mihca, Ed Beach, miunduay. (mapatay i 1996 a mihca)
